text: Edmundo Vlinder was a footballer from Curacao. Vlinder competed at the 1952 Summer Olympics. He was born on 6 February 1926 and died on February 2009.Eddy Vlinder == References == Category:1926 births Category:2009 deaths Category:Curaçao footballers Category:Curaçao Olympians
